These are Puzzles for 4x7 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 4x7-Level-2-1::.
There are 7 different favourite beverages: 7up, coffee, fanta, juice, soy-milk, sprite, tea
7 different brands of cigars are smoked: prince, havana, oliveros, davidoff, bluemaster, chaman, fonseca
The people prefer 7 different types of sport: baseball, basketball, cricket, golf, skateboarding, surfing, swimming
City: san-francisco, new-york, colone, nizza, prague, berlin, liverpool
 1. the person who's sport is golf is on the far right##1
 2. the person who's sport is skateboarding is the davidoff-smoker##1
 3. the person traveling to prague is the person who's sport is cricket##1
 4. the havana-smoker is on the left of the person traveling to berlin##1
 5. the prince-smoker is on the right of the fonseca-smoker##1
 6. the person drinking coffee is the person who's sport is cricket##1
 7. the person traveling to liverpool is on the right of the bluemaster-smoker##1
 8. the person traveling to nizza is between the person traveling to liverpool and the chaman-smoker##2
 9. the bluemaster-smoker is on the right of the person traveling to colone##1
10. the person drinking fanta is in the middle##1
11. the person who's sport is baseball is the person drinking soy-milk##1
12. the person drinking soy-milk is the person traveling to san-francisco##1
13. the person drinking 7up is on the left of the oliveros-smoker##1
14. the chaman-smoker is the person traveling to colone##1
15. the person traveling to berlin is on the left of the fonseca-smoker##1
16. the person drinking coffee is on the left of the person drinking sprite##1
17. the person who's sport is surfing is on the left of the oliveros-smoker##1
18. the person drinking tea is on the right of the bluemaster-smoker##1
19. the person who's sport is swimming is on the right of the person traveling to new-york##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |       2       |    3     |     4      |     5     |    6     |    7    |
| Beverage      | coffee  | sprite        | soy-milk | fanta      | juice     | 7up      | tea     |
| Cigar   | havana | davidoff         | fonseca   | prince | chaman    | bluemaster | oliveros |
| Sport         | cricket | skateboarding | baseball | basketball | swimming  | surfing  | golf    |
| City     | prague  | berlin         | san-francisco     | new-york    | colone | nizza     | liverpool     |

