 9. the person who's sport is badminton is on the left of the person drinking 7up##1
10. the fan of metal is between the fan of indie and the person who's birthday is in july##2
11. the fan of disco is the person who's birthday is in february##1
12. the fan of pop is on the left of the fan of reggae##1
13. the fan of pop is between the person who's birthday is in july and the fan of reggae##2
14. the person drinking mirinda is on the left of the person who's sport is cricket##1
